<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.5.9">
<l>kaḷḷak kuḻaviyāyk kālāl cakaṭattai</l>
<l>taḷḷi yutaittiṭṭut tāyāy varuvāḷai</l>
<l>meḷḷat toṭarntu piṭittā ruyiruṇṭa</l>
<l>vaḷḷalē koṭṭāy cappāṇi</l>
<l rend="indent">mālvaṇṇaṉē koṭṭāy cappāṇi.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having toppled a huge cart kicking out with [your] foot,</l>
<l>Liberal [lord] who, as a disguised infant,</l>
<l>Quietly approaching and grabbing the one who came as a mother,</l>
<l>Consumed her dear life, clap your hands;</l>
<l rend="indent">dark-hued one, clap your hands!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
